[Adapted from Jinjiang Wenxuecheng's
"Queen Liu Heipang", written by Ge Yang]

21
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:39,470
[The Legendary Life of Queen Lau]

22
00:01:40,070 --> 00:01:40,403
[Episode 11]

23
00:01:40,403 --> 00:01:42,350
[This work is fictitious.
Any resemblance to reality is coincidental]

24
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:47,080
Your Majesty,

25
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:49,760
are you really not going

26
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:51,800
to let Her Majesty attend
your birthday banquet this year?

27
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,720
This year's birthday banquet
is different from the previous years'.

28
00:01:54,879 --> 00:01:56,680
It isn't just a feast this time.

29
00:01:57,239 --> 00:01:59,000
It may not be a good thing for her to show up.

30
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:01,400
So are you saying you'll let Her Majesty...

31
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,480
Stop asking too many questions.

32
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:17,679
A tyrant! A bully! Unreasonable!

33
00:02:17,679 --> 00:02:18,399
A fatuous ruler!

34
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,039
Your Majesty,

35
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:23,279
you've been scolding him all day.

36
00:02:23,839 --> 00:02:24,759
Did I get to scold him?

37
00:02:24,759 --> 00:02:26,360
He already left before I did.

38
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:27,479
I can't scold him in person.

39
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:28,800
Can't I scold his substitute?

40
00:02:29,279 --> 00:02:30,240
All right.

41
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:32,039
I'll pretend I don't hear anything.

42
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:34,880
Your Majesty,

43
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:37,240
this clay doll looks like you.

44
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,720
Are you molding yourself and the Emperor?

45
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:41,000
Stop right there!

46
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,639
I'm not, so don't overthink.

47
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:44,039
I'm molding a couple of clay dolls

48
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:45,960
because Yunyan insisted.

49
00:02:46,160 --> 00:02:47,320
I need some favor from her.

50
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:48,520
So I reluctantly agreed to do this.

51
00:02:50,679 --> 00:02:51,360
Your Majesty,

52
00:02:51,399 --> 00:02:53,679
what favor are you asking from Princess Yunyan?

53
00:02:54,199 --> 00:02:56,320
I'm thinking of asking Yunyan
to bring some maidservants here

54
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,399
to renovate the Western Cold Palace

55
00:02:57,399 --> 00:02:58,639
starting tomorrow.

56
00:02:59,000 --> 00:02:59,919
A renovation?

57
00:03:00,399 --> 00:03:02,559
But didn't we just repair the roof?

58
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:03,880
That's not enough.

59
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,639
I've thought about this for a while now.

60
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:07,240
Since Duan Yunzhang is not letting us out of here,

61
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,759
we'll just turn Western Cold Palace into a place

62
00:03:08,759 --> 00:03:10,960
where even deities would refuse to leave.

63
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:29,660
[Taihe Hall]

64
00:03:47,220 --> 00:03:49,900
[Taihe Hall]

65
00:03:52,639 --> 00:03:54,199
The auspicious hour has arrived!

66
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:56,279
May the ceremony begins!

67
00:04:07,039 --> 00:04:07,639
Your Majesty,

68
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:11,240
I'm afraid the Grand Chancellor won't be coming.

69
00:04:11,759 --> 00:04:12,600
Let's wait a little longer.

70
00:04:12,919 --> 00:04:13,919
Wait again?

71
00:04:14,479 --> 00:04:16,839
We mustn't miss the auspicious hour.

72
00:04:17,359 --> 00:04:20,239
If Your Majesty's
coming-of-age ceremony is delayed,

73
00:04:20,239 --> 00:04:22,880
your officials can't afford
to bear the responsibility.

74
00:04:23,839 --> 00:04:24,519
Your Majesty,

75
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:25,959
how about this?

76
00:04:26,239 --> 00:04:29,839
Allow me to put on the crown for you
on behalf of the Grand Chancellor.

77
00:04:29,839 --> 00:04:30,640
What do you think?

78
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:31,679
Don't bother.

79
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:34,679
I shall wait for the Grand Chancellor's arrival
no matter what.

80
00:04:43,239 --> 00:04:43,880
Zhang,

81
00:04:45,320 --> 00:04:46,839
are you not going to proceed with the ceremony

82
00:04:47,399 --> 00:04:49,040
if the Grand Chancellor doesn't come today?

83
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,839
Grand Tutor Wei is the Emperor's teacher.

84
00:04:52,799 --> 00:04:53,839
Listen to me

85
00:04:54,119 --> 00:04:55,359
and let him put the crown on you.

86
00:04:55,559 --> 00:04:56,839
Mother, don't persuade me.

87
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,720
I've made up my mind.

88
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,480
Pass my order.

89
00:05:01,839 --> 00:05:03,239
We shall pick another auspicious day
for the coming-of-age ceremony.

90
00:05:08,519 --> 00:05:10,320
The Grand Chancellor has arrived!

91
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:25,799
My apologies for coming late.

92
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:28,239
I hope for Your Majesty's pardon.

93
00:06:04,230 --> 00:06:06,160
[Taihe Hall]
On this auspicious day,

94
00:06:07,079 --> 00:06:09,399
the crown is added.

95
00:06:10,359 --> 00:06:12,559
It brings glory to the ancestors.

96
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:15,399
May the Emperor's coming-of-age ceremony

97
00:06:15,679 --> 00:06:17,559
brings the will to enrich the people

98
00:06:17,799 --> 00:06:19,720
and prosperity to the country.

99
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,839
Blessings for all over the world

100
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:24,600
throughout the ages!

101
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:35,559
To celebrate the success
of the Western Cold Palace's renovation,

102
00:06:35,559 --> 00:06:37,839
everyone can enjoy an unlimited supply

103
00:06:37,839 --> 00:06:39,359
of liquor and meat skewers!

104
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,920
We may have missed out

105
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,720
on the Emperor's birthday this year.

106
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,040
But I didn't expect we get

107
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,519
to eat to our hearts' content here!

108
00:06:45,799 --> 00:06:47,959
Yunzhang deals with many problems every day
that he overlooked things here.

109
00:06:47,959 --> 00:06:49,279
Today, my sister-in-law will treat

110
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:49,839
everyone well!

111
00:06:49,839 --> 00:06:51,399
Make yourself at home!

112
00:06:51,399 --> 00:06:53,119
Raise your wine cup

113
00:06:53,119 --> 00:06:54,519
and drink it all!

114
00:06:54,519 --> 00:06:56,239
We still have many meat skewers.

115
00:06:56,239 --> 00:06:59,559
Don't be shy!

116
00:07:07,300 --> 00:07:08,540
[Yufang Garden]

117
00:07:08,679 --> 00:07:11,440
We wish Your Majesty perpetual peace

118
00:07:11,559 --> 00:07:13,119
and long life.

119
00:07:15,390 --> 00:07:16,550
[Yufang Garden]
Please rise.

120
00:07:16,559 --> 00:07:18,040
Thank you, Your Majesty.

121
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:19,720
I treat

122
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:21,200
all of you as my family.

123
00:07:21,799 --> 00:07:22,959
So you can drop the formalities.

124
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,559
Please take your seat.

125
00:07:27,079 --> 00:07:28,480
Thank you, Your Majesty.

126
00:07:31,839 --> 00:07:33,519
Prince Yunchong presented

127
00:07:33,519 --> 00:07:36,279
a handmade Iron Peach Leaf Fan.

128
00:07:36,839 --> 00:07:38,920
I made this personally for you.

129
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,160
It's called Iron Peach Leaf Fan.

130
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:42,399
I hope it can protect you.

131
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,600
I hope your life is smooth sailing

132
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:45,839
and I wish Your Majesty longevity.

133
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:47,839
You're too kind.

134
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:51,640
Take a seat.

135
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:58,160
Princess Yunyan presented
a pair of happy couple figurines.

136
00:08:01,559 --> 00:08:02,839
Why is Princess Yunyan not here

137
00:08:02,839 --> 00:08:04,600
on my birthday?

138
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:05,640
I heard

139
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:07,600
Princess Yunyan went to the Western Cold Palace.

140
00:08:07,839 --> 00:08:08,720
To meet the Queen?

141
00:08:09,079 --> 00:08:09,839
Do you want me

142
00:08:09,839 --> 00:08:11,720
to send someone to fetch Princess Yunyan here?

143
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:13,079
No need.

144
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:16,359
Let her bother the Queen would be good.

145
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,200
Let's continue.

146
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:23,079
The officials' presents are as below.

147
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:26,079
Scholar Xu presented a jade pillow.

148
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:30,079
Grand Protector Liu presented one pearl.

149
00:08:30,959 --> 00:08:32,239
Censor Wang presented

150
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:35,679
a gilded pheasant enamel amphora.

151
00:08:52,670 --> 00:08:54,910
[Yufang Garden]
I wish Your Majesty good health

152
00:08:54,919 --> 00:08:56,919
and the Donghao Empire prosperity and peace.

153
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:04,119
Grand Chancellor,

154
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:05,799
what is this?

155
00:09:07,119 --> 00:09:09,479
This is a gift I prepared for Your Majesty.

156
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:11,080
[Gift List]
You can pick

157
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,799
any items you want from the gift booklet.

158
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,919
You're so generous.

159
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:24,080
There are more gifts on this list

160
00:09:25,039 --> 00:09:28,440
than all the officials' presents combined.

161
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:31,080
Don't let it trouble you.

162
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:34,840
I've received a lot of gifts

163
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:36,280
in recent years.

164
00:09:36,559 --> 00:09:39,320
These are just nothing compared to what I have.

165
00:09:39,479 --> 00:09:41,239
I don't feel any losses

166
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,559
even if I give them all to you, Your Majesty.

167
00:09:45,520 --> 00:09:46,599
What did he mean by that?

168
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,880
Is he showing off

169
00:09:50,039 --> 00:09:52,200
that he has amassed great wealth?

170
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:52,919
Don't worry.

171
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,760
He behaved so insolently.

172
00:09:54,760 --> 00:09:56,400
His Majesty will punish him severely.

173
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:58,239
If he gets even unruly, just have his head.

174
00:10:00,239 --> 00:10:01,599
Thank you for your generosity.

175
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,640
But I don't need these.

176
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:07,119
All these are good items.

177
00:10:07,119 --> 00:10:08,200
Won't it be a pity

178
00:10:08,679 --> 00:10:09,799
if you don't want them?

179
00:10:11,159 --> 00:10:12,840
I only want one thing.

180
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,880
Something that was originally mine.

181
00:10:16,359 --> 00:10:17,919
I wonder if you're willing to give it to me.

182
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,919
What are you going to do

183
00:10:21,679 --> 00:10:23,000
if I refuse?

184
00:10:42,340 --> 00:10:45,300
[Yufang Garden]

185
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:54,320
I shall fight you for it until the end.

186
00:10:55,559 --> 00:10:58,440
From today on, I shall ever obey you.

187
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:02,440
Let alone allow you to abuse your power
to cover up the truth.

188
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,080
You of all people?

189
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,440
I may not be able to do it today.

190
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:11,479
I shall wait for next year.

191
00:11:12,239 --> 00:11:13,320
Even if I still can't do it next year,

192
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:14,799
I shall wait for the coming years.

193
00:11:15,239 --> 00:11:16,599
As long as I'm alive,

194
00:11:17,239 --> 00:11:19,000
I'll never give up.

195
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,640
Aren't you afraid

196
00:11:23,479 --> 00:11:24,440
that I never intend

197
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:26,239
to let you live until that day?

198
00:11:27,359 --> 00:11:28,080
Insolence!

199
00:11:33,919 --> 00:11:34,559
I am.

200
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:36,880
I'm terrified.

201
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,479
But after giving it some thought,

202
00:11:41,239 --> 00:11:44,000
if my words can never carry

203
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,479
any weight in the future,

204
00:11:46,479 --> 00:11:47,960
I'd rather die.

205
00:11:52,679 --> 00:11:55,039
It's your birthday today.

206
00:11:55,359 --> 00:11:57,400
So I can't humiliate you here.

207
00:11:58,159 --> 00:12:00,520
What you're asking from me is nothing more

208
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:02,880
than taking over the reins.

209
00:12:03,239 --> 00:12:04,280
Correct?

210
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:04,880
Correct.

211
00:12:05,679 --> 00:12:06,640
How about this?

212
00:12:08,110 --> 00:12:11,000
[Yufang Garden]
The imperial examination is after half a month.

213
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:13,880
I'm sure

214
00:12:14,599 --> 00:12:16,799
you know better than me
about the Late Emperor's will.

215
00:12:17,239 --> 00:12:19,520
I don't have to repeat
what's written in the posthumous edict.

216
00:12:20,239 --> 00:12:21,520
Are you saying

217
00:12:22,239 --> 00:12:25,760
if I can accomplish what's stipulated
in the Late Emperor's posthumous edict

218
00:12:26,559 --> 00:12:28,359
and rank in the top three in the examination,

219
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,719
you'll hand over the reins to me?

220
00:12:31,119 --> 00:12:31,880
Exactly.

221
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:37,000
You won't pull any kind of tricks, will you?

222
00:12:39,359 --> 00:12:41,159
You're right about that.

223
00:12:42,039 --> 00:12:45,880
I've always acted and spoken as I wanted.

224
00:12:46,359 --> 00:12:47,679
I might deny

225
00:12:48,119 --> 00:12:49,599
what I've said after a while.

226
00:12:51,039 --> 00:12:52,960
My, my. What should I do about it?

227
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:55,479
Something bad had happened!

228
00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:58,359
Thick smoke is billowing
around Western Cold Palace!

229
00:12:58,359 --> 00:12:59,320
A fire must have broken out!

230
00:13:00,559 --> 00:13:01,200
Guards!

231
00:13:01,599 --> 00:13:02,239
Put out the fire!

232
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:03,000
Yes, Your Majesty!

233
00:13:07,799 --> 00:13:09,239
Come and have some more.

234
00:13:09,559 --> 00:13:10,400
Sister-in-law,

235
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:12,080
let me light the crackers to get rid of bad luck.

236
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:13,200
Hurry, light it over there.

237
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:13,760
All right.

238
00:13:14,119 --> 00:13:14,760
Let's roast more.

239
