485
00:23:04,800 --> 00:23:05,359
We can't.

486
00:23:05,520 --> 00:23:06,719
Father told me to stay in the palace,

487
00:23:07,239 --> 00:23:08,160
so I can't go back.

488
00:23:08,479 --> 00:23:09,239
I can't leave.

489
00:23:14,199 --> 00:23:14,719
Fengyue,

490
00:23:14,880 --> 00:23:16,560
what's going on?

491
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:18,239
I heard

492
00:23:18,439 --> 00:23:20,800
many concubines and maidservants died
at the Cold Palace.

493
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,959
Could that be their spirits

494
00:23:22,959 --> 00:23:24,040
making all the noise?

495
00:23:24,560 --> 00:23:25,880
Don't scare me!

496
00:23:30,199 --> 00:23:31,119
Feng... Fengyue,

497
00:23:31,119 --> 00:23:32,199
go and check it out.

498
00:23:32,199 --> 00:23:33,319
-I'm scared.
-It's all right.

499
00:23:33,319 --> 00:23:34,719
Go now.

500
00:23:55,400 --> 00:23:56,959
Fengyue, leave.

501
00:24:04,040 --> 00:24:04,880
Liu Baiyu.

502
00:24:05,439 --> 00:24:06,520
Why are you here at this late hour?

503
00:24:18,359 --> 00:24:18,839
What...

504
00:24:19,119 --> 00:24:20,079
What do you want to do?

505
00:24:20,479 --> 00:24:21,719
We're both Father's daughters.

506
00:24:21,719 --> 00:24:23,319
You better don't do anything reckless.

507
00:24:23,479 --> 00:24:25,319
I especially prepared this rat poison.

508
00:24:25,479 --> 00:24:26,239
Rat poison?

509
00:24:26,239 --> 00:24:27,079
Liu Baiyu,

510
00:24:27,520 --> 00:24:28,920
you'll get what you wished for.

511
00:24:29,199 --> 00:24:30,839
You want to be the Queen, don't you?

512
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,680
I can help you fulfill your wish.

513
00:24:33,439 --> 00:24:34,680
The Queen?

514
00:24:38,760 --> 00:24:39,359
Did you see

515
00:24:39,359 --> 00:24:40,839
how scared you were just now?

516
00:24:41,160 --> 00:24:42,119
This rat poison

517
00:24:42,119 --> 00:24:43,760
is for the rats here.

518
00:24:43,959 --> 00:24:45,479
I was putting an act at Xiangluo Hall just now.

519
00:24:45,479 --> 00:24:46,560
You fell for it, didn't you?

520
00:24:46,959 --> 00:24:48,599
Others may see it as me oppressing you.

521
00:24:48,599 --> 00:24:49,719
But the truth is I was supporting you.

522
00:24:49,719 --> 00:24:51,199
My goal

523
00:24:51,199 --> 00:24:52,800
is to help you gain sympathy and love from others.

524
00:24:55,439 --> 00:24:56,959
I'm sure you're putting an act now.

525
00:24:57,079 --> 00:24:57,839
I won't believe you.

526
00:24:58,319 --> 00:24:59,640
I'm not lying to you now.

527
00:25:00,319 --> 00:25:01,680
I'll just make it clearer.

528
00:25:02,119 --> 00:25:03,079
I'll take today's incident, for example.

529
00:25:03,079 --> 00:25:04,479
I realized

530
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:06,560
that as long as I'm in the Imperial Palace,

531
00:25:06,560 --> 00:25:08,319
I'll have no human rights and freedom.

532
00:25:08,319 --> 00:25:09,560
I'll always be ordered about

533
00:25:09,560 --> 00:25:10,920
by Liu Xie and Duan Yunzhang.

534
00:25:11,319 --> 00:25:12,199
So I've decided

535
00:25:12,199 --> 00:25:13,040
to fight back.

536
00:25:13,040 --> 00:25:14,560
I'll make them fight among themselves

537
00:25:14,560 --> 00:25:15,920
while I control my own fate.

538
00:25:15,920 --> 00:25:17,239
I want those who want to stay to remain here,

539
00:25:17,239 --> 00:25:18,560
while those who want otherwise to go.

540
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:20,760
What do you mean?

541
00:25:21,479 --> 00:25:22,479
That means to let you stay here,

542
00:25:22,479 --> 00:25:23,400
so I can leave.

543
00:25:24,560 --> 00:25:25,719
Your method is too inefficient.

544
00:25:25,719 --> 00:25:26,760
I need to help you to speed it up.

545
00:25:26,920 --> 00:25:28,719
The earlier you become the Queen,

546
00:25:28,719 --> 00:25:30,079
the sooner I can leave the palace.

547
00:25:31,479 --> 00:25:33,160
Are you serious

548
00:25:33,160 --> 00:25:34,479
about helping me?

549
00:25:34,719 --> 00:25:36,439
Don't you like His Majesty at all?

550
00:25:37,880 --> 00:25:38,599
How do I put this?

551
00:25:38,599 --> 00:25:40,280
Duan Yunzhang does have his strengths.

552
00:25:40,280 --> 00:25:42,839
He's serious about being an emperor.

553
00:25:43,280 --> 00:25:45,040
He's studious and not a fool.

554
00:25:45,280 --> 00:25:46,599
He's also polite to the servants.

555
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:49,359
He is good-looking too.

556
00:25:50,199 --> 00:25:51,160
But what's the point of all these?

557
00:25:51,280 --> 00:25:53,000
He prefers fine liquor and women,

558
00:25:53,000 --> 00:25:54,599
while I prefer a simple life.

559
00:25:54,599 --> 00:25:56,640
We're not fated to be together.

560
00:25:58,560 --> 00:26:00,079
Why are you still hesitating?

561
00:26:00,680 --> 00:26:02,199
You're just scared of Liu Xie, right?

562
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:03,880
In any case, Liu Xie only needs a daughter

563
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:04,800
to become the Queen.

564
00:26:04,800 --> 00:26:06,040
There's no difference
if either one of us becomes one.

565
00:26:06,520 --> 00:26:07,959
Besides, you're more obedient.

566
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:11,160
Are you serious?

567
00:26:12,920 --> 00:26:14,199
As long as we join hands,

568
00:26:14,280 --> 00:26:15,119
we will make it.

569
00:26:19,319 --> 00:26:20,520
What should we do now?

570
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:23,119
No need to whisper. There's no one else here.

571
00:26:23,760 --> 00:26:24,280
Oh, you're right.

572
00:26:25,640 --> 00:26:28,079
We must have a plan first.

573
00:26:28,199 --> 00:26:29,160
When he shows up,

574
00:26:29,160 --> 00:26:30,479
I'll slap you.

575
00:26:30,479 --> 00:26:31,599
After that, you'll go into his arms

576
00:26:31,599 --> 00:26:32,640
and cry...

577
00:26:36,380 --> 00:26:39,220
[Imperial Academy]

578
00:26:41,359 --> 00:26:42,839
Greetings, Your Majesty.

579
00:26:44,439 --> 00:26:45,839
Can I get up now?

580
00:26:47,959 --> 00:26:48,719
Rise.

581
00:26:50,000 --> 00:26:51,520
(She's behaving strangely today.)

582
00:26:52,680 --> 00:26:54,160
What brings you two here?

583
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:57,520
We're also His Majesty's study companions.

584
00:26:58,760 --> 00:27:00,160
Oh, it's your side job.

585
00:27:00,319 --> 00:27:02,680
I won't let you snatch my position that easily.

586
00:27:03,520 --> 00:27:06,479
These two may not have
good academic achievements,

587
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:09,239
but they're better than you

588
00:27:09,760 --> 00:27:11,839
when it comes to literacy.

589
00:27:12,920 --> 00:27:13,920
Yes, you're right.

590
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:16,599
I know we have a huge gap between us.

591
00:27:16,680 --> 00:27:18,520
So to catch up with you,

592
00:27:18,599 --> 00:27:19,920
I have a study companion too.

593
00:27:21,239 --> 00:27:23,119
A study companion like you
have a study companion too?

594
00:27:30,839 --> 00:27:32,239
Greetings, Your Majesty.

595
00:27:34,400 --> 00:27:35,079
What were you doing?

596
00:27:35,079 --> 00:27:36,400
Why are you only here now?

597
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:38,239
Are you my study companion
or am I your study companion?

598
00:27:38,560 --> 00:27:39,880
Why are you talking lasciviously?

599
00:27:39,880 --> 00:27:41,319
Are you trying to seduce His Majesty?

600
00:27:41,560 --> 00:27:42,119
I...

601
00:27:42,479 --> 00:27:43,880
(What are these two up to?)

602
00:27:44,479 --> 00:27:46,199
(Are they trying to disrupt my studies)

603
00:27:46,199 --> 00:27:47,239
(by delaying me with their disputes?)

604
00:27:48,959 --> 00:27:50,000
(I'll never fall for that.)

605
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:52,599
Stop looking! Hold this!

606
00:27:59,199 --> 00:28:00,199
Wait, why is he...

607
00:28:00,199 --> 00:28:01,040
Remember this.

608
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:03,520
I'm now the jealous queen who's bullying you,

609
00:28:03,520 --> 00:28:05,560
while you're the damsel
waiting for His Majesty to save you.

610
00:28:05,959 --> 00:28:06,839
Just wait and see.

611
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,319
His Majesty will take pity on you,

612
00:28:08,319 --> 00:28:10,079
help you, and fall in love with you.

613
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:11,680
Let's go to class.

614
00:28:11,760 --> 00:28:12,280
All right.

615
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:14,040
Hurry up, Baiyu!

616
00:28:14,040 --> 00:28:15,479
Stop wasting time!

617
00:28:17,119 --> 00:28:18,400
I'll get a seat for you.

618
00:28:18,959 --> 00:28:19,479
Let's go.

619
00:28:23,520 --> 00:28:24,000
I...

620
00:28:25,479 --> 00:28:26,400
There's a rat!

621
00:28:27,520 --> 00:28:27,839
Where is it?

622
00:28:27,839 --> 00:28:28,640
Over there.

623
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:29,560
It ran away.

624
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:30,560
Baiyu,

625
00:28:30,760 --> 00:28:32,040
you better study well

626
00:28:32,040 --> 00:28:33,479
since you have got a nice spot.

627
00:28:37,040 --> 00:28:37,680
Sister-in-law,

628
00:28:38,119 --> 00:28:39,560
this is my seat.

629
00:28:40,760 --> 00:28:41,680
Is your name written on it?

630
00:28:42,599 --> 00:28:43,880
It's against the rules.

631
00:28:43,880 --> 00:28:44,959
What rules?

632
00:28:46,439 --> 00:28:47,199
Liu Baiyu, you better get up.

633
00:28:47,199 --> 00:28:48,040
What are you doing?

634
00:28:48,400 --> 00:28:48,920
You fox!

635
00:28:48,920 --> 00:28:50,160
Who are you calling a fox?

636
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:51,640
She's here to disrupt Yunzhang's studies!

637
00:28:51,760 --> 00:28:52,680
Can't she just sit here?

638
00:28:52,800 --> 00:28:54,479
This seat doesn't have your name on it.

639
00:28:54,680 --> 00:28:55,000
Stay away from here.

640
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:56,199
-But...
-Don't touch me!

641
00:28:56,199 --> 00:28:56,839
I must sit here.

642
00:28:56,839 --> 00:28:58,239
You're making a scene

643
00:28:58,239 --> 00:28:59,280
and disrupting His Majesty from studying.

644
00:28:59,280 --> 00:29:00,239
I didn't do that.

645
00:29:00,239 --> 00:29:01,719
Sister-in-law, I must sit here.

646
00:29:09,040 --> 00:29:10,160
Just sit over there.

647
00:29:10,160 --> 00:29:11,119
I'm here to help Yunzhang with his studies.

648
00:29:11,119 --> 00:29:12,040
-Don't come any closer!
-No!

649
00:29:12,040 --> 00:29:12,880
I'm here to help Yunzhang with his studies!

650
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:13,959
Why can't you sit there?
Is this seat made of gold?

651
00:29:13,959 --> 00:29:15,400
I'm really here to help Yunzhang with his studies!

652
00:29:15,400 --> 00:29:16,199
Enough talking!

653
00:29:16,400 --> 00:29:17,160
Your Highness!

654
00:29:20,760 --> 00:29:21,800
Who is fighting here?

655
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:25,000
Grand Tutor Wei.

656
00:29:26,439 --> 00:29:27,000
She...

657
00:29:28,280 --> 00:29:29,599
Your Majesty.

658
00:29:30,760 --> 00:29:32,199
As the Queen of the nation

659
00:29:32,199 --> 00:29:33,079
and a woman of nobility,

660
00:29:33,079 --> 00:29:34,439
how can you openly bully the prince

661
00:29:34,439 --> 00:29:35,640
in the academy?

662
00:29:35,640 --> 00:29:36,599
Moreover,

663
00:29:36,959 --> 00:29:38,880
he's your brother-in-law.

664
00:29:39,359 --> 00:29:40,400
That's not what happened, Grand Tutor Wei.

665
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:41,119
Let me explain.

666
00:29:41,119 --> 00:29:42,599
It's just a misunderstanding.

667
00:29:42,599 --> 00:29:43,719
Explain what?

668
00:29:44,239 --> 00:29:45,880
Facts speak louder than words.

669
00:29:46,760 --> 00:29:48,079
I've long heard

670
00:29:48,479 --> 00:29:50,760
that the Queen is ungrateful, eccentric,

671
00:29:50,760 --> 00:29:51,880
and deviant.

672
00:29:52,400 --> 00:29:53,719
I didn't believe it.

673
00:29:53,959 --> 00:29:54,959
After seeing you today,

674
00:29:56,040 --> 00:29:57,239
you're such a disappointment.

675
00:29:57,359 --> 00:29:58,959
I feel sorry and hurt for you.

676
00:30:00,800 --> 00:30:02,959
Did you think I dare not punish you

677
00:30:03,520 --> 00:30:05,000
because you're the Queen?

678
00:30:05,439 --> 00:30:05,959
No.

679
00:30:06,199 --> 00:30:08,239
You may be the Queen.

680
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:09,560
But

681
00:30:09,839 --> 00:30:12,479
even if your father,
the Grand Chancellor, is here,

682
00:30:12,479 --> 00:30:14,359
he'll still have to give me some face.

683
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:18,599
It would be best if one mends their ways.

684
00:30:20,079 --> 00:30:22,040
Put out your hand.

685
00:30:23,760 --> 00:30:24,479
I won't admit it!

686
00:30:24,880 --> 00:30:25,880
Even if I did something wrong,

687
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:27,719
it's all because I love His Majesty too much.

688
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:29,680
You love me too much?

689
00:30:31,599 --> 00:30:32,880
I'll say it again.

690
00:30:33,760 --> 00:30:35,400
Put out your hand.

691
00:30:38,839 --> 00:30:39,439
Your Majesty,

692
00:30:40,079 --> 00:30:42,040
I may not be partial to anyone in my duties.

693
00:30:42,359 --> 00:30:43,280
I do know

694
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:46,000
the justification
that a pampered wife is a virtuous wife.

695
00:30:46,239 --> 00:30:49,560
So you'll have to bear the punishment

696
00:30:51,560 --> 00:30:55,040
of having your palm being hit
on Her Majesty's behalf.

697
00:30:57,760 --> 00:30:59,040
Thank you for coming to my rescue, Your Majesty.

698
00:31:03,280 --> 00:31:03,920
Do it.

699
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:05,040
Yes, Your Majesty.

700
00:31:18,680 --> 00:31:19,400
Stop hitting him!

701
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:23,400
Who are you?

702
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:27,359
Grand Tutor Wei,

703
00:31:27,800 --> 00:31:29,760
I'm Her Majesty's study companion.

704
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:30,959
May I be bold to say this?

705
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:32,880
It is inappropriate

706
00:31:34,479 --> 00:31:35,119
for you to do this.

707
00:31:35,560 --> 00:31:36,800
I can't believe a mere study companion

708
00:31:36,800 --> 00:31:38,359
is trying to question me.

709
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:40,719
Please enlighten me, then.

710
00:31:40,959 --> 00:31:42,800
What was your original aspiration
as a grand tutor?

711
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:43,680
Original aspiration?

712
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:47,760
My original aspiration is based on,
"There'll be fire if you strike the stone,

713
00:31:47,760 --> 00:31:49,560
and there'll be no smoke if you don't."

714
00:31:51,359 --> 00:31:53,680
Since the Late Emperor
entrusted the Imperial Academy

715
00:31:53,680 --> 00:31:54,760
to me

716
00:31:54,760 --> 00:31:57,319
and bestowed me this Imperial Ruler,

717
00:31:58,199 --> 00:32:00,400
I shall not be unworthy of the Late Emperor.

718
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:02,680
I'll always use it

719
00:32:02,680 --> 00:32:04,479
to beat you into shape

720
00:32:04,839 --> 00:32:07,599
and help you have an upright and clear sight.

721
00:32:08,359 --> 00:32:10,920
What an abusive way to help one
have an upright and clear sight.

722
00:32:11,760 --> 00:32:13,959
Her Majesty is indeed wrong
to make a scene in the academy.

723
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:15,959
But you declared Her Majesty guilty

724
00:32:15,959 --> 00:32:18,719
entirely based on what you saw
without finding the cause.

725
00:32:19,119 --> 00:32:21,079
May I be bold to ask if you have a clear sight?

726
00:32:22,079 --> 00:32:23,880
You advised His Majesty to pamper his wife.

727
00:32:24,119 --> 00:32:26,359
But His Majesty and Her Majesty
are not getting along.

728
00:32:26,560 --> 00:32:28,079
Yet, you let His Majesty take the punishment

729
00:32:28,079 --> 00:32:31,239
on Her Majesty's behalf
just because you wish to do so.

730
00:32:31,560 --> 00:32:34,160
May I be bold to ask again
if your conduct is upright?

731
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:37,280
"There'll be fire if you strike the stone,

732
00:32:37,280 --> 00:32:38,439
and there'll be no smoke if you don't"

733
00:32:38,439 --> 00:32:40,680
is a metaphor used by Mr. Dongye

734
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:41,719
to advise students to study.

735
00:32:42,199 --> 00:32:44,040
What he's trying to express is

736
00:32:44,199 --> 00:32:45,560
that knowledge comes from learning.

737
00:32:45,719 --> 00:32:47,040
Knowledge doesn't come without effort.

738
00:32:47,479 --> 00:32:48,319
He's trying to emphasize

739
00:32:48,400 --> 00:32:51,040
that one can only gain knowledge from studying.

740
00:32:51,400 --> 00:32:53,640
One does not gain knowledge from beating.

741
00:32:55,040 --> 00:32:57,880
Grand Tutor Wei,
you take its meaning out of context

742
00:32:58,079 --> 00:32:59,599
as a teacher at the palace.

743
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:03,439
Do you not do enough scholarly research?

744
00:33:04,959 --> 00:33:06,560
Who exactly are you?

745
00:33:08,520 --> 00:33:09,640
I'm Liu Baiyu.

746
00:33:09,880 --> 00:33:10,839
Apart from her study companion,

747
00:33:11,040 --> 00:33:12,920
I'm also Her Majesty's elder sister.

748
00:33:14,359 --> 00:33:15,000
Enough.

749
00:33:15,760 --> 00:33:17,239
Grand Tutor Wei, punish me if you want.

750
00:33:17,439 --> 00:33:18,599
If you don't, let's start the class.

751
00:33:19,359 --> 00:33:20,479
Stop wasting time.

752
00:33:20,479 --> 00:33:21,119
Your Majesty,

753
00:33:21,359 --> 00:33:23,520
didn't you see how Baiyu helped you?

754
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:27,479
I didn't have to be punished.

755
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:30,040
It's all because of you.

756
00:33:35,640 --> 00:33:36,199
It's all right.

757
00:33:37,800 --> 00:33:39,160
Go back to your seats

758
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:40,400
and get back to study!

759
00:33:48,160 --> 00:33:48,719
Here.

760
00:33:51,920 --> 00:33:52,560
Sister-in-law,

761
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:54,079
where should I sit then?

762
00:33:54,199 --> 00:33:55,160
You can sit anywhere you want.

763
00:34:06,800 --> 00:34:07,479
Don't be seen.

764
00:34:07,479 --> 00:34:08,600
Don't let the Consort Dowager sees us.

765
00:34:08,600 --> 00:34:09,280
All right.

766
00:34:12,280 --> 00:34:13,159
Sister-in-law!

767
00:34:13,870 --> 00:34:14,560
[Chonghua Hall]
Yunyan?

768
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:16,040
What brings you to Chonghua Hall?

769
00:34:16,679 --> 00:34:17,760
I injured Yunchong

770
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:18,879
at the Imperial Academy during the day.

771
00:34:18,879 --> 00:34:20,000
So I come to see how he's doing.

772
00:34:23,040 --> 00:34:23,959
Yunyan!

773
00:34:23,959 --> 00:34:25,719
Please let me see Yunchong.

774
00:34:25,719 --> 00:34:26,560
Huh? What?

775
00:34:26,560 --> 00:34:27,320
Stop me from going in.

776
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:27,959
Yunzhang is here.

777
00:34:27,959 --> 00:34:28,719
Your brother.

778
00:34:30,239 --> 00:34:30,760
No!

779
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:31,800
I will never let you get close

780
00:34:31,800 --> 00:34:33,080
to Yunchong today!

781
00:34:36,320 --> 00:34:37,239
(Why is she here?)

782
00:34:38,040 --> 00:34:39,760
(Don't tell me she's waiting especially for me.)

783
00:34:40,120 --> 00:34:40,760
Princess Yunyan,

784
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:42,159
just let me see him.

785
00:34:42,639 --> 00:34:43,719
Liu Jinfeng,

786
00:34:43,719 --> 00:34:45,600
I've misjudged you.

787
00:34:45,719 --> 00:34:47,399
I never knew you could be this ruthless.

788
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:50,040
Not only did you banish your sister
to the Cold Palace,

789
00:34:50,320 --> 00:34:51,719
but you also picked on my brother.

790
00:34:52,040 --> 00:34:53,600
I will never give you the chance

791
00:34:53,600 --> 00:34:54,760
to bully him again!

792
00:34:55,080 --> 00:34:55,679
Yunyan,

793
00:34:56,239 --> 00:34:58,280
do you really think I'm a ruthless person?

794
00:34:58,719 --> 00:34:59,879
Do you really think I wanted

795
00:34:59,879 --> 00:35:00,959
to send my sister to the Cold Palace?

796
00:35:01,439 --> 00:35:03,280
It's all your brother, the Emperor's fault.

797
00:35:04,199 --> 00:35:04,879
(My fault?)

798
00:35:05,399 --> 00:35:06,120
(Why is it my fault?)

799
00:35:08,080 --> 00:35:09,800
I hated Duan Yunzhang.

800
00:35:10,239 --> 00:35:11,919
But when I see him and Baiyu
exchanging flirty glances at each other,

801
00:35:11,919 --> 00:35:12,879
I get so upset.

802
00:35:13,399 --> 00:35:14,320
I get jealous.

803
00:35:15,479 --> 00:35:17,239
I couldn't even control myself.

804
00:35:17,239 --> 00:35:18,600
What else could I do?

805
00:35:20,320 --> 00:35:21,399
(Don't tell me she really fell in love with me)

806
00:35:21,399 --> 00:35:22,760
(as she said at the Imperial Academy)

807
00:35:23,439 --> 00:35:24,320
(during the day?)

808
00:35:28,190 --> 00:35:29,710
[Chonghua Hall]
Why are you causing a ruckus at this late hour?

809
00:35:32,360 --> 00:35:33,840
You were punished on my behalf today.

810
00:35:34,080 --> 00:35:35,239
Take these medicinal herbs.

811
00:35:36,159 --> 00:35:36,840
What?

812
00:35:37,280 --> 00:35:37,959
Yunzhang,

813
00:35:38,159 --> 00:35:39,919
you were punished in her stead?

814
00:35:40,320 --> 00:35:41,199
No such thing.

815
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:42,320
Don't listen to her nonsense.

816
00:35:44,520 --> 00:35:46,159
What evil thoughts are you thinking

817
00:35:46,159 --> 00:35:47,600
for banishing your sister to the Cold Palace?

818
00:35:50,120 --> 00:35:51,080
Did you just scold me?

819
00:35:52,639 --> 00:35:54,000
You were all smiles with her

820
00:35:54,439 --> 00:35:55,639
but so fierce with me.

821
00:35:57,120 --> 00:35:58,600
Could it be that you're feeling sorry for her?

822
00:36:00,479 --> 00:36:02,600
Could it be that you want
to go to the Cold Palace to see her?

823
00:36:03,120 --> 00:36:04,120
Could it be that you'll change

824
00:36:04,360 --> 00:36:06,120
the Western Cold Palace
to the Western Warm Palace?

825
00:36:07,439 --> 00:36:08,639
If you go and see her today,

826
00:36:08,760 --> 00:36:10,439
I'll jump into this Taiyuan Pond.

827
00:36:10,639 --> 00:36:11,639
I mean what I say.

828
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:14,560
I've sworn an oath

829
00:36:15,120 --> 00:36:17,760
that you'll only love me in this life.

830
00:36:17,959 --> 00:36:20,360
You can never depose me or take in consorts.

831
00:36:21,120 --> 00:36:22,879
(The Queen has lost her senses.)

832
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:24,600
(It looks like I have to believe)

833
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:26,360
(that I'm absolutely charming.)

834
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:28,959
(She may have resisted in many ways before,)

835
00:36:29,439 --> 00:36:30,879
(but she still fails to resist)

836
00:36:30,879 --> 00:36:32,000
(such a temptation.)

837
00:36:32,639 --> 00:36:34,639
(Now she's being irrational because of love.)

838
00:36:35,120 --> 00:36:36,080
(How pitiful.)

839
00:36:36,959 --> 00:36:39,120
Taiyuan Pond is too shallow for you to die.

840
00:36:39,360 --> 00:36:40,360
Are you a fool?

841
00:36:41,120 --> 00:36:42,239
I'm going to visit Yunchong.

842
00:36:42,600 --> 00:36:43,600
Yunyan, watch her

843
00:36:43,600 --> 00:36:44,600
and don't let her wander off.

844
00:36:47,639 --> 00:36:48,520
What does this mean?

845
00:36:50,560 --> 00:36:52,479
(I behaved like a shrew just now.)

846
00:36:52,479 --> 00:36:53,600
(I was acting hysterically.)

847
00:36:53,600 --> 00:36:55,120
(I'm sure he hates me a lot now.)

848
00:36:55,280 --> 00:36:56,639
(Hurry and let me scare you away,)

849
00:36:56,639 --> 00:36:58,439
(so you'll go into the arms of Baiyu.)

850
00:37:02,479 --> 00:37:03,840
Your Highness, please endure.

851
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:04,439
Gently, please.

852
00:37:04,439 --> 00:37:05,520
Three. Two.

853
00:37:07,520 --> 00:37:08,360
Oh, my.

854
00:37:09,840 --> 00:37:10,439
Your Highness,

855
00:37:10,639 --> 00:37:11,520
how do you feel now?

856
00:37:16,120 --> 00:37:16,760
Are you all right now?

857
00:37:18,360 --> 00:37:18,959
I can't believe it.

858
00:37:18,959 --> 00:37:19,560
I'm fine now.

859
00:37:20,320 --> 00:37:21,000
You can leave now.

860
00:37:21,360 --> 00:37:21,919
Yes, Your Highness.

861
00:37:21,919 --> 00:37:22,600
Remember.

862
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:24,120
Don't let my mother know about this.

863
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:25,840
Yes, Your Highness.

864
00:37:26,080 --> 00:37:27,280
I shall take my leave now.

865
00:37:28,439 --> 00:37:29,080
Go.

866
00:37:30,320 --> 00:37:31,639
It's all that jinx's fault.

867
00:37:32,040 --> 00:37:33,439
She almost killed me.

868
00:37:35,120 --> 00:37:37,520
Jinfeng is indeed rash and rude.

869
00:37:38,639 --> 00:37:39,959
It's my fault.

870
00:37:40,639 --> 00:37:41,239
Yunzhang,

871
00:37:41,760 --> 00:37:42,760
I was talking about Liu Baiyu.

872
00:37:45,120 --> 00:37:45,800
You see?

873
00:37:46,120 --> 00:37:47,479
You're taking her side.

874
00:37:48,760 --> 00:37:49,479
Liu Baiyu stood up for you

875
00:37:49,479 --> 00:37:51,120
at the Imperial Academy today

876
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:52,520
because she wanted to get on your good side.

877
00:37:53,120 --> 00:37:53,639
Of course,

878
00:37:53,639 --> 00:37:55,399
Sister-in-law is behaving strangely lately.

879
00:37:56,080 --> 00:37:57,280
She's becoming scarier.

880
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:01,040
Do you think I don't know all these?

881
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:04,879
But it's not their fault.

882
00:38:04,879 --> 00:38:06,639
I'm the one to blame.

883
00:38:08,439 --> 00:38:09,639
What does this have to do with you?

884
00:38:09,879 --> 00:38:10,959
How is it not related to me?

885
00:38:12,600 --> 00:38:14,239
It's my fault for being too charming

886
00:38:14,639 --> 00:38:17,120
that both women lost their rationality
because of me.

887
00:38:18,080 --> 00:38:18,639
I should be blamed.

888
00:38:19,959 --> 00:38:20,560
Yunzhang,

889
00:38:20,560 --> 00:38:22,120
is that a joke?

890
00:38:22,120 --> 00:38:23,479
How is it a joke?

891
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:24,760
Didn't you see

892
00:38:25,639 --> 00:38:27,879
how Jinfeng mistreated Liu Baiyu today?

893
00:38:28,080 --> 00:38:30,120
Liu Baiyu may appear to be silently enduring it.

894
00:38:30,520 --> 00:38:32,040
But you can see she has set her sights on me

895
00:38:32,040 --> 00:38:33,560
and is prepared to seduce me at any time.

896
00:38:34,040 --> 00:38:35,040
If this goes on,

897
00:38:35,120 --> 00:38:36,520
how am I going to study

898
00:38:37,280 --> 00:38:38,639
if a fight really breaks out between them?

899
00:38:41,239 --> 00:38:41,959
Yunchong,

900
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:43,919
I have a task for you.

901
00:38:44,439 --> 00:38:45,639
From tomorrow on,

902
00:38:45,959 --> 00:38:48,080
you'll be responsible
for keeping an eye on Liu Baiyu

903
00:38:48,320 --> 00:38:50,120
to reduce her contact with the Queen.

904
00:38:50,320 --> 00:38:50,959
While I

905
00:38:51,120 --> 00:38:53,560
will be responsible
for reducing Jinfeng's anger

906
00:38:53,840 --> 00:38:54,919
with my charm.

907
00:38:55,120 --> 00:38:56,439
This will prevent the conflict

908
00:38:56,439 --> 00:38:57,760
between them from happening at the root.

909
00:38:57,760 --> 00:38:59,040
Then we can create

910
00:38:59,120 --> 00:39:00,760
a good learning environment.

911
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:01,639
Me?

912
00:39:01,800 --> 00:39:03,040
Keep an eye on Liu Baiyu?

913
00:39:03,639 --> 00:39:04,560
No way.

914
00:39:05,080 --> 00:39:07,239
Are you going

915
00:39:07,479 --> 00:39:08,639
to watch them torment me?

916
00:39:09,080 --> 00:39:10,639
What if I get poor results in the examination?

917
00:39:14,399 --> 00:39:15,360
Fine.

918
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:17,120
I'll do my best for you.

919
00:39:18,120 --> 00:39:19,320
That's more like it.

920
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:22,639
Liu Baiyu,

921
00:39:23,520 --> 00:39:25,399
you better watch it.

922
00:39:32,479 --> 00:39:33,120
Shuan,

923
00:39:34,040 --> 00:39:34,639
deliver my edict.

924
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:38,239
Say that I sympathize with the Queen
for renovating the Western Cold Palace.

925
00:39:39,159 --> 00:39:41,639
From now on, Western Cold Palace
will be changed to Western Warm Palace.

926
00:39:41,879 --> 00:39:45,000
It'll be Liu Baiyu's temporary residence
in the palace.

927
00:39:45,520 --> 00:39:47,120
Is there a meaning to this, Your Majesty?

928
00:39:47,120 --> 00:39:48,840
Isn't it obvious enough?

929
00:39:49,879 --> 00:39:51,840
Liu Baiyu isn't one of my concubines.

930
00:39:52,040 --> 00:39:53,600
She doesn't have the right
to stay at the Cold Palace.

931
00:39:53,800 --> 00:39:54,879
If this gets out to those who don't know,

932
00:39:54,879 --> 00:39:56,760
they would think she's involved with me.

933
00:39:57,560 --> 00:39:58,959
I don't want such a misunderstanding.

934
00:39:58,959 --> 00:40:01,120
If you change the name,

935
00:40:01,280 --> 00:40:02,600
aren't you afraid Her Majesty might think

936
00:40:02,600 --> 00:40:04,120
you're making advances on Miss Baiyu?

937
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:06,639
It's all right if she misunderstands.

938
00:40:06,959 --> 00:40:09,000
She'll be having a sleepless night

939
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:10,120
with her heart dissipating in the air.

940
00:40:10,800 --> 00:40:12,080
When she finds out about this tomorrow,

941
00:40:12,080 --> 00:40:13,639
she'll be extremely happy

942
00:40:14,120 --> 00:40:15,439
and wild with joy.

943
00:40:16,120 --> 00:40:16,639
Go now.

944
00:40:27,800 --> 00:40:28,600
What did I tell you?

945
00:40:28,639 --> 00:40:29,840
Men just won't admit it.

946
00:40:30,040 --> 00:40:31,760
It was during the day
he treated you indifferently yesterday.

947
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:34,120
And he changed the name of the Cold Palace
on the same night.

948
00:40:34,120 --> 00:40:35,239
You need to work harder today.

949
00:40:35,239 --> 00:40:36,639
You might conquer him.

950
00:40:37,120 --> 00:40:37,760
Go.

951
00:40:44,120 --> 00:40:44,760
Your Majesty,

952
00:40:44,760 --> 00:40:46,120
thank you for changing the Western Cold Palace

953
00:40:46,120 --> 00:40:47,360
to Western Warm Palace.

954
00:40:58,239 --> 00:40:58,919
Liu Baiyu,

955
00:40:59,280 --> 00:41:00,520
you can just sit here.

956
00:41:01,800 --> 00:41:03,360
Why? This isn't my seat.

957
00:41:03,439 --> 00:41:05,080
Do other seats have your name on them?

958
00:41:05,399 --> 00:41:06,360
It's against the rules.

959
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:07,600
What rules?

960
00:41:07,600 --> 00:41:08,399
But that's...

961
00:41:09,320 --> 00:41:10,679
Don't disturb Yunzhang from studying.

962
00:41:43,740 --> 00:41:46,660
♪Only second to the Emperor♪

963
00:41:46,660 --> 00:41:50,620
♪Anyone who's against it should back off♪

964
00:41:50,620 --> 00:41:53,660
♪I'll make a face and fear no heaven and earth♪

965
00:41:53,660 --> 00:41:57,460
♪I'll let you go for now♪

966
00:41:57,460 --> 00:41:59,820
♪I'm not a motherly model♪

967
00:41:59,820 --> 00:42:01,660
